Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.49,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}铛铛地响起了声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.95,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}从心底溢了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:47.25,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}想象被世界渐渐敲响
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:51.75,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}呐呐、告诉我古怪未来的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:56.09,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}再次迷惘之时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:59.72,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}还会在这里等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:12.44,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}今天的夏风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:14.82,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}又将你给我的衣服的风帽
