Comment: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,————————Text-PartA————————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:38.91,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.16,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙要让人等到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.41,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,到底干什么才能那么花时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:46.79,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.63,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,从那家伙出去已经过去多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:50.88,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,三天！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:52.71,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:54.84,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙到底有多蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:59.64,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,再说那家伙应该也是被村民排斥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.56,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,慢吞吞如果再出了什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:04.60,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,别生气别生气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:09.19,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈要穿的…婚纱来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:13.07,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是找那个花了很多时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.28,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:17.36,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样也没办法了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.95,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算是这样也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:25.54,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,他的寿命也没有长到可以这样挥霍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:33.34,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  爸爸不是说会一起来  永远在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.01,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈不幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.22,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,当然幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:41.80,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再稍微等一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:50.02,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  时间静止的世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.06,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里会是什么感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:54.90,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样？妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.53,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.25,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,这种地方竟然有房子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:13.29,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的距离为什么到现在都没人发现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.25,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(930,990)}TSUKIHIKO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.25,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是掳走少年兵的怪物的腹地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:22.51,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是少年兵那家伙说怪物是自己的妻子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:25.35,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物是少年兵的妻子？怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:29.93,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是怪物用妖术操纵了少年兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:34.56,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,想要通过操纵少年兵  有朝一日袭击村子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.02,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果变成那样只能够处理掉少年兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:40.28,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你们听好  趁早干完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.87,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.62,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你磨蹭个什么  走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.29,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:55.13,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…刚才好像有脚步声…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.00,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸回来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.34,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,少年兵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.80,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(813,990)}SHION
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.80,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:08.72,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉了吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:11.43,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  果断一发解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.90,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.81,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这是怪物的女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.65,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}妈妈…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.57,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那头发  肯定没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.69,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  把这家伙也干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:25.36,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…喂  她还很小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.95,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.83,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,磨磨蹭蹭的搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.95,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  让我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.62,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目隐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.25,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？！消失了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.59,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…妖术？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:38.71,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.68,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.22,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.47,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目欺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.19,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目夺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.48,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.58,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,东躲西藏也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.79,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,纵使逃至天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:16.21,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,尔等所在之处也立可知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.79,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,少年兵怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:19.88,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:25.38,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿直言则读透汝心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:27.59,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目窃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:33.85,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快说怪物在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:38.40,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不然…我们也不想打你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:42.19,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…也不能放任来历不明的东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:46.61,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(741,990)}AZAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:46.61,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,薊…薊是我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.07,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不准…出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:52.58,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  为什么要包庇那个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.25,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你是人类吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:58.04,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,还要反抗的话…不会轻饶你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:00.13,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不是包庇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.63,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不是全部说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:07.97,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和她…和家人永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:09.47,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.05,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:14.72,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！似乎发现信号一类的东西了  一直延续到森林那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.02,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:20.61,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,是少年兵为回去而准备的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.94,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,立即为退治怪物做准备！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:26.44,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多给我清醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.36,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,把她解决掉后  你也会清醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.20,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快点做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:32.70,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.62,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:38.91,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,滚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.08,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.13,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,然后永远不许带任何人来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.72,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了就赶快给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.14,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,少年兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:08.94,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.53,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.62,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,别再靠近我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:18.50,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再因我而让你们受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.62,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.29,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:24.67,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,想要逃避世间之理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:27.84,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,并且还把你们也牵连进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.80,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,其实已经意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.80,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有我在就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:41.52,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,只要没有我  你们就能在这个世界上幸福地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.90,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我没有祈盼幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.82,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,只是稍微做了一会梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:52.53,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,能永远和家人生活在一起的幻想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.20,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,太美好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.70,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真是无可救药得美好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.75,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:04.25,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  你不是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.63,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要使用这种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.88,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我没有这样说的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:14.93,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,但你要作为一个人类  和父亲一起幸福地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.35,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我的…幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:21.02,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！妈妈别走！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:26.40,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  对不起  对不起  对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.57,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,永远爱你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:34.57,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我会永远祈祷你们能幸福  永远…
Comment: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,————————Text-PartB————————
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉这样不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又想要擅自出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  别说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你读连环画
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是哦  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到这里一起读吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天就读这个故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天开始  从妈妈留下我们消失那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底过了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸去世的时候  茉莉呱呱坠地的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈都没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈现在也在那个没有终结的世界一个人生活着么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一人等待着不知会不会归来的妈妈也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等茉莉再大些  就让她见见外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界肯定会接受她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像妈妈对我所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在对我来说茉莉的幸福就是我的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  不知道什么时候睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:10:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！在就应答我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？喂  怪物不是说只有一只吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别老想着以前的传说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也靠它找到了有意思的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊  这头发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候做成展示品的话肯定能大赚一笔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼  住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个  放开那孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？区区个怪物说点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实点！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  要把他也一起抓了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你在听我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  妈妈  我们…没有变得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到  连她们也拉进这边了  您真是坏心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个永不结束的世界的痛苦您不是最清楚的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  不会闭嘴的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺从于利己又轻松的欲望  创造出这个世界的不正是大人您吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来您的愿望是把最爱的家人一起带到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是很好嘛  女儿和孙女一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿望终于实现了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起  真是愚蠢  没错  没错  就要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是我们的最大的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  这都是我的错  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  就是这个表情  太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  对  就是这样  变成这种悲剧全都是因为您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少  至少只有这孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己丢掉了女王蛇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那个附身的话  确实能救那孩子一命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这样也就没有抑制这个世界的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附身于您的蛇失去了女王是多么的混乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放心吧  至少不会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您对这世界所下达的把8月15日逝去的生命卷进来这条命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是无法停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  要是不离家出走就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且都是修哉不好  都是修哉欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不听使唤地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  你和家人走散了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我也和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色的眼睛也是一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  不要再走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁…来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是…女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都是一个人  好寂寞  一个人好寂寞啊  谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来  不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到我眼睛的话就会变成石头的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…我必须得是一个人  所以请回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼唤我的人就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  我和你是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都被别人忌讳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全用不着害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…那个…做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  我睡着了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  他去哪里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都太过分了  把我丢下一起走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有人在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗  会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口…口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  请喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不烫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  嗯  不烫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害  你是从哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在那里睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢  不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  记性不怎么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记性不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也经常忘记东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然觉得要是能都记得就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个  我还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么  是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要朋友  想和朋友一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋…友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  但是我只记得这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和朋友一起玩耍  只有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就和我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以介绍我的朋友给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…大家一定很乐意…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经深夜0时了  还有如此人群
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信  到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如您所见  非常的吵闹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  能听到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:20:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上是从现场发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也去吧  大家一定都在那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的朋友
Comment: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,————————Text-PartC————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女失去了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的重要的朋友  全都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女一个人哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想再一次和大家一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女无数次如此祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么向少女搭话了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实现您的愿望吧  实现您的渴望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为您带来一个能实现您的空想的世界吧
